This is a minimalistic Arch Linux theme for SLiM.
It is based on the Minimal Debian SLiM theme by Pasteurized:
http://pasteurized.deviantart.com/art/Minimal-Debian-SLiM-theme-146727470

Themes are stored in:
/usr/share/slim/themes

SLiM configurations are stored in:
/etc/slim.conf

